'''苏州新加坡国际学校'''（{{lang-en|Suzhou Singapore International School}}，SSIS）是一所位于[[江苏省|江苏省]][[苏州市|苏州]][[苏州工业园区|工业园区]]的[[国际学校|国际学校]]，创立于1996年6月。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.moe.gov.cn/publicfiles/business/htmlfiles/moe/moe_506/200503/6243.html|title = 教育部公布经批准设立的外籍人员子女学校名单|accessdate = 2012-11-21|author = 中华人民共和国教育部|date = |publisher = |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121103122030/http://www.moe.edu.cn/publicfiles/business/htmlfiles/moe/moe_506/200503/6243.html|archive-date = 2012-11-03|dead-url = yes}}</ref>学校提供从学前教育至12年级，提供[[國際文憑大學預科課程|国际文凭]]（IB）和[[高級中學|高中]]文凭（HSD）方案。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ssis-suzhou.net/explore/index.aspx|title=SSIS: Explore  WHO WE ARE|accessdate=2015-08-21|author=|date=|publisher=|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820174529/http://www.ssis-suzhou.net/explore/index.aspx|archivedate=2016-08-21}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://sipedu.sipac.gov.cn/website/Item/36083.aspx|title = 苏州新加坡国际学校|accessdate = 2012-12-06|author = 苏州工业园区教育局|date = |publisher = |language = en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://edu.sina.com.cn/ischool/2014-10-29/1048440862.shtml|title = 年薪十万不够付1年学费 盘点苏州“土豪”学校|accessdate = 2014-10-29|author = |date = |publisher = }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://eng.2500sz.com/eng/listing-show.asp?id=209|title = Suzhou Singapore International School 苏州新加坡国际学校|accessdate = 2015-07-10|author = 名城苏州|date = |publisher = |language = en}}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

